{"tid":592120,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（劣改） 情人節不要獻醜","createTime":"2018-03-14T03:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T09:46:37.000Z","uid":12851,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5e669bd8901aa8a3edbe68b38593a6ad806efa07","tid":592120,"uid":12851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"情人節不要獻醜<br />\n躺於家似隻狗<br />\n開心的你不要令我更兜踎<br />\n難道我非你不嫁<br />\nFF都應抖下<br />\n青春戀愛只出於手裡漫畫<br />\n<br />\n其實我知你缺點<br />\n單戀偏卻上演<br />\n這種感覺很痛如何能避免<br />\n成日說公廁公廁<br />\n手都無拖幾次<br />\n心酸打句：mk仔先要殘廁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n曾經很深信小李 踢出個未來食到春野<br />\n怕只怕小櫻的心已經有屬<br />\n無奈是我是路人 其實我只是路人 <br />\n誰人能告訴我主角的興奮<br />\n<br />\n肥絲也得到真愛 這個地球 愈變荒誕<br />\n訓一覺 起身番工 發霉照舊<br />\n無奈是我沒情人 誰人令我靜寂呆等<br />\n<br />\n軟弱的身分 無女的走過一生<br />\n我沒法擁吻<br />\n我祈求安慰<br />\n去雞竇求其執劑<br />\n佢話我好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec737874ac7555baba0770fe25e0b3d0623bdd51","tid":592120,"uid":171523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"30e343c3ce10766fa36f782fedc76ea028371ec3","tid":592120,"uid":12851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T20:07:28.000Z","msg":"毒撚無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c35c7143cb5701131de823069526cff7186b9bd","tid":592120,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T20:22:51.000Z","msg":"好撚慘 毒撚開post真係無人理<br />\n<br />\nBtw 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c6dba89813d166deb8d48650e9f83f3a171365","tid":592120,"uid":47709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T22:19:09.000Z","msg":"唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a4c77fc18f2f2c8784b7a1cc69a237355541ec","tid":592120,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T22:23:4